# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# IMPORTANT: site_data.db is intentionally NOT ignored.
# It must be committed to the repo so the roadmap's history
# persists across every automated GitHub Actions run. If it's
# gitignored, each daily run starts with an empty database and
# the roadmap will only ever show that day's single new issue.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
